snippet.title: C9 | Launch Trailer | Continent of the Ninth Seal | Webzen MMORPG
snippet.description:
Time to Break the Seal!
C9 is kicking off with the official launch! (http://c9.webzen.com)

C9 (Continent of the Ninth Seal) is an upcoming action MORPG that casts players as heroes in the world of Glenheim, a place broken into nine continents and threatened by the evil designs of the villain known as Nefer. Featuring precision controls usually found only on consoles, a variety of skill combos and play styles, and strong RPG elements, C9 caters not just to fans of action games, but appeals to everyone.

Enjoy official trailer movie and start C9!
http://us.webzen.com/Download/C9
